data.description: Looking for your own personal oasis in Hillborough County? Look no further than this stunning home boasting 0.93 acres of private land! Relax and unwind in the small commercial pool complete with an 8 person spa and stunning blue mosaic brick surrounding. With concrete foundation and six-block construction.    Step inside and enjoy the luxury of a French door leading to the master bedroom, complete with a sitting room and walk-in closet with a washer and dryer hookup. Want to make it even more luxurious? This space can easily be converted to include a shower.    Entertain guests in the converted study, complete with a sink and little bar for added convenience. You'll love the sleek ceramic flooring throughout the home, and the kitchen's granite countertops make meal prep a breeze.    With so much to offer, this home is sure to impress. Don't miss out on the chance to make it yours today!
